---
description: TypeScript conventions for the storefront
globs: "**/*.ts,**/*.tsx"
---

Use type-only imports for types. Zod schemas live next to the API route
that owns them and infer their TypeScript types — never write a type by
hand when a schema exists. Discriminated unions over boolean flags for
component props. Barrel files are banned in app/ because they defeat
tree-shaking.
